api_list.name: Enhancer 4k
api_list.description:
Image Enhancer API.
API enhances image with 4K resolution i.e. 2,048 x 1,080 pixels.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://enhancer-api.p.rapidapi.com/rapidapi/enhancer/4k"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "enhancer-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
